<ol>
    <li><h3 id="AI_integration"><a href="#main_features">AI Integration with the Site:</a></h3> Integrates the ability to search internal resources, external resources, and add information to the local system.</li>
    <li><h3 id="modular_design"><a href="#main_features">Modular Design:</a></h3> Ensures the site is built in a modular fashion for ease of maintenance and scalability.</li>
    <li><h3 id="todo_project_management_logs"><a href="#main_features">ToDo, Project Management, Logs:</a></h3> Incorporates tools for managing tasks, projects, and maintaining logs for better tracking and management.</li>
    <li><h3 id="admin_functions"><a href="#main_features">Admin Functions:</a></h3> Provides capabilities to edit files, control CSS, update the application, and manage the schema.</li>
    <li><h3 id="security"><a href="#main_features">Security:</a></h3> Implements robust security measures to protect data and user information.</li>
    <li><h3 id="documentation"><a href="#main_features">Documentation:</a></h3> Maintains comprehensive documentation to assist developers and users.</li>
    <li><h3 id="search"><a href="#main_features">Search:</a></h3> Uses AI to build a comprehensive information base, improving search accuracy and relevance.</li>
    <li><h3 id="reference_system"><a href="#main_features">Reference System of Documents:</a></h3> Offers a well-organized system for managing and referencing documents.</li>
    <li><h3 id="power_monitoring"><a href="#main_features">Power Monitoring System:</a></h3> Includes a system for monitoring power usage and efficiency.</li>
    <li><h3 id="web_based_email"><a href="#main_features">Web-Based Email:</a></h3> Provides a web-based email client for managing emails.</li>
    <li><h3 id="web_based_calendar"><a href="#main_features">Web-Based Calendar:</a></h3> The application now includes a web-based calendar module. This module can be used by all other modules in the application for scheduling and event management. It provides features such as creating, viewing, and editing events, setting reminders, and sharing events with other users. The calendar module is designed to be flexible and adaptable, allowing it to be integrated with other modules in various ways. For example, the project management module could use the calendar to schedule project deadlines and milestones, while the education module could use it to schedule classes and exams.</li>
    <li><h3 id="web_based_address_book"><a href="#main_features">Web-Based Address Book:</a></h3> Maintains a web-based address book for contact management.</li>
