    <li><h3 id="web_based_music_player"><a href="#main_features">Web-Based Music Player:</a></h3> Includes a web-based music player for playing and managing music files.</li>
    <li><h3 id="hosting_multiple_sites"><a href="#main_features">Hosting Multiple Sites:</a></h3> Supports the ability to host multiple sites using the same software.</li>
    <li><h3 id="extensive_herbal_health_info"><a href="#main_features">Extensive Herbal and Health Information:</a></h3> Provides detailed information on herbs and health-related topics.</li>
